340
00:13:50.514 --> 00:13:51.154
Vamos,

341
00:13:51.394 --> 00:13:53.235
¿de modo que tú conocías a la vieja?

342
00:13:53.820 --> 00:13:54.860
Todo

343
00:13:54.860 --> 00:13:56.540
