344
00:13:57.020 --> 00:13:57.980
Ah, sí,

345
00:13:58.460 --> 00:13:59.900
Sofía Ivanovna.

346
00:14:00.220 --> 00:14:01.740
Sofía Semenovna,

347
00:14:01.900 --> 00:14:03.580
