355
00:14:18.505 --> 00:14:19.465
a Rascónicov.

356
00:14:20.025 --> 00:14:20.745
Ea, vamos,

357
00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:22.960
dijo Rascónicov,

358
00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:25.680
