407
00:16:18.070 --> 00:16:21.589
Todo mundo ignorado surgía confusamente en su alma.

408
00:16:22.389 --> 00:16:24.630
Recordó de pronto que Raskolnikov

409
00:16:24.630 --> 00:16:26.630
