445
00:17:41.789 --> 00:17:42.429
alguien.

446
00:17:43.470 --> 00:17:45.549
Era a Sonia a quien esperaba.

447
00:17:46.190 --> 00:17:48.429
Bien pronto la vio despedirse de los 2

448
00:17:48.429 --> 00:17:50.190
